{"tid":1660573,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(重要)林鄭施政報告同留言係重要文宣","createTime":"2019-10-17T14:44:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T11:53:37.000Z","uid":244653,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"f380cddffdb7a3f682c792c0a85e401430eaa0db","tid":1660573,"uid":244653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T14:44:39.000Z","msg":"今日帶大家睇babykingdom同yahoo<br />\n申請最高九成按揭貸款的樓價上限由四百萬元倍增至八百萬元<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jcPjmgw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjcPjmgw.png&h=f17e3070&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c2r51gb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc2r51gb.png&h=030b14c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sGy0Qak.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsGy0Qak.png&h=7f1589ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n回應單程證配額問題 特首：新來港人士提供更多勞動力<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8O9zaaX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8O9zaaX.png&h=4ca2b6e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林鄭月娥：暫時不考慮完全禁止内地人購買香港物業<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mss1zCG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMss1zCG.png&h=46420d99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你地見到咩?我明白大家好想大眾關注黑狗,但我地抗爭既核心重有政府無能<br />\n<br />\n經歷三個月文宣,狗既問題早就人盡皆知,剩反既人唔係藍絲就係港豬,你淨同距講黑警殺人,根本距地就唔care,所以要將黑警同政府無能掛勾<br />\n<br />\n例如cut150個内地人,作為長期在babykingdom睇水既人,我可以肯定距地實支持,點解唔做文宣?<br />\n<br />\n我地要赢,就冇可避免要接觸這類人,從文宣打開缺口就係好方法<br />\n<br />\n利申:紅土人,見到周圍文宣成日被撕,覺得同紅土長者講黑狗根本冇用,不如貼政府施政無能既文宣?<br />\n<br />\n有冇人識整,art零分"},{"pid":"6c25ba189f64c5062ee6512e45807bfa9ca224de","tid":1660573,"uid":47605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T14:44:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zBif5mg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzBif5mg.jpg&h=44757529&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"7fe9d59d9